    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Guardrail node backed by session string storage. Blocks turns whose human message matches a pattern in the storage. Resolution priority (factory): named string_storage → inline_strings → server-wide default (default-guardrail-patterns.txt from server-config). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
